headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Monolithic Power Systems After Its 65% Rally in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering what to do with Monolithic Power Systems stock as it sits near its all-time highs, you are not alone. After all, it is not every day a company rises 17.7% in a single month and racks up an impressive 65.2% year-to-date return. Even over the past five years, this stock has delivered a staggeringly strong 225.7%. Clearly, something is energizing investor optimism, likely a mix of accelerating demand across diverse end markets and broad enthusiasm for semiconductor suppliers...
